{"tid":1388043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2013年 烏克蘭革命 示威者舉起鏡對住班警","createTime":"2019-07-30T15:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T13:49:46.000Z","uid":140535,"like":62,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e842fdc5015f64140e8ad78fef0f0af0db577e06","tid":1388043,"uid":140535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:44:20.000Z","msg":"Protestors in Ukraine use mirrors to show militarized police what they have become. Police around the world need to take a good hard look in the mirror and decide if they serve the people or their corrupt governments.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.artifacting.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Mirror-Protest.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fwww.artifacting.com%2Fblog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F01%2FMirror-Protest.jpg&h=1ad4aa00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://futuristrendcast.files.wordpress.com/2016/09/ukraine-mirror-protests-grannies-police.jpg?w=604\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffuturistrendcast.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F09%2Fukraine-mirror-protests-grannies-police.jpg%3Fw%3D604&h=ede10fec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加塊鏡有冇得諗"},{"pid":"d2adb862b01e2ecd4f46e8e00594fdd0a218f250","tid":1388043,"uid":36612,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:46:19.000Z","msg":"發覺依幾次都有好多老人家上前線做和理非 勸極都唔走<br />\n既然勸唔掂佢地唔好上去 叫佢地拎塊鏡其實都有得諗"},{"pid":"142ffa89d4b5e116ac27d34feafe5f704d95b481","tid":1388043,"uid":43806,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:50:46.000Z","msg":"其實拎塊鏡真係有用 <br />\n1)反燈光照射 <br />\n2)人係最衝動嘅時間見到自己個樣會停一停"},{"pid":"31822bab778e180052afbb91665b82160b55d3cc","tid":1388043,"uid":36073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:10:36.000Z","msg":"和理非去IKEA 買塊鏡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51dea482e2acc895ad6d5bb85eb70d9c102b25fe","tid":1388043,"uid":21501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:13:05.000Z","msg":"14年唔係用過咩"},{"pid":"dcb1290c47bc0fc309f8d01dd0b1b39f497bbb8f","tid":1388043,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:13:48.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選應要排最頭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私咁，過埋2047都死左啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"f4bc51b4cad63197c043e3fb424f3d210a546670","tid":1388043,"uid":70510,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"142ffa89d4b5e116ac27d34feafe5f704d95b481","tid":1388043,"uid":43806,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:50:46.000Z","msg":"其實拎塊鏡真係有用 <br />\n1)反燈光照射 <br />\n2)人係最衝動嘅時間見到自己個樣會停一停"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:20:57.000Z","msg":"3)舉耐左發現原來班狗真係冇人性, 一野好似飛碟咁橫向擲過去又得, 唔洗浪費"},{"pid":"07dfe6dfc8c09ad41ab63ab4f9e6cbb23090f787","tid":1388043,"uid":259710,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:2